{
  "texts": [
    "This approach might be especially suitable to include in cloud and edge-computing IDS platforms where high scalability and fast response times are desired.",
    "However, the fuzzy clustering is not devoid of some demerits some of which includes; the higher computational complexity as the datasets size increases and the handling of highly imbalanced data set.",
    "These can be alleviated using sampling technique like SMOTE and use of parallel processing for faster computations so as to make the model stronger in the dynamic network environment.",
    "This proposed model can be easily implemented with cloud and edge computing systems that form the basis of practical IDS solutions.",
    "SaaS solutions exist to offer an easily scalable environment for a variety of functions related to analyzing large amounts of network traffic data and delivering updates."
  ]
}